{"tid":291444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Trump贏咗】中國解禁准牛肉入口 美國爭回$195億市場 僅限30月齡以下","createTime":"2017-06-20T14:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T04:41:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a5f3006a236253682b0a6a28f26681dd82c8da","tid":291444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"2017年06月20日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170620/large/1497959733_6e4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170620%2Flarge%2F1497959733_6e4c.jpg&h=97c467f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國家質檢總局公佈，即日起允許美國牛肉進口，這是自2003年12月美國爆發瘋牛症後，中國再次全面允許美國牛肉進口。分析認為這是美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）的一次勝利，重新打開這個估計有25億美元（約195億港元）的市場，同時亦可扭轉中美巨額的貿易差距。<br />\n<br />\n大陸國家質檢總局發出公告，正式允許美國牛肉輸陸，這次開放輸入中國的牛肉，還包括牛心、腎、肝、瓣胃、牛筋，但不包括扁桃線、迴腸未端、免治牛肉和用機械分離的牛肉，同時限定是30月齡以下剔骨和帶骨的牛肉。公告又列舉針對牛肉的來源、質素、包裝、檢驗檢疫程序等多項要求，如要求牛肉必須在美國屠宰、在大陸口岸入境時不得檢出有禁藥等。<br />\n<br />\n美國對中國的貿易逆差去年達3,470億美元（約2.7萬億港元），特朗普上任後認為急需要將差距收窄，中國國家主席習近平今年4月訪問美國時，中美雙方達成的協議當中，幫助美國牛肉企業進入中國，是其中一項。<br />\n中國在2003年禁令前，是美國牛肉的最大市場，雖然中國當局禁止美國牛肉進口，可是中國人卻對美國牛肉需求十分巨大，不少美國牛肉都是經香港走私到大陸，以供應內地龐大市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170620/56854374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170620%2F56854374&d=0s4k466Ec1exW3L0JB69mp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f1758b92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170620%2F56854374&h=b3039534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170620/56854374</a>"},{"pid":"6c636990af6ce5e37a36769cf1d0ec3b26285c7b","tid":291444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49e9b75034ade57eec54ef866b817fffaa0e397","tid":291444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"美國最鍾意周圍出口牛肉。<br />\n<br />\n韓農成日示威就係反對政府向美國開放市場；台灣蔡英文都講過，為左同盟關係，牛肉入口問題上美國嘅立場就係佢嘅立場"},{"pid":"4d1db4ae7dd5bdaae6fae321d5eb2e8f5c3809a9","tid":291444,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"TRUMP做一年已經勁撚過奧巴馬8年"},{"pid":"3fab272616d0e593674e96507184de5b62871fb4","tid":291444,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TRUMP做一年已經勁撚過奧巴馬8年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMAGA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaec71b4c189bd77d46bf4b7fbcf024d3cd6dedf","tid":291444,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"一車車牛牛送入鄰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0a68fa15f44e9beaa37e7f67c30a3e9b823cf7","tid":291444,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"糧食入口大國"},{"pid":"2c1f115b317dbd9ebdc35f7440097ba820911e36","tid":291444,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一車車牛牛送入鄰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼可以做隻美國牛鬼"},{"pid":"b8465319386dff69cf619b6e2ff780028fb41682","tid":291444,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"支共為左一中政策<br />\n<br />\n連貿易額都要出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb02ad4c7c796be4947c2a29e5d7e7c5fe3fb9","tid":291444,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"牛肉 + 豬肉精 &gt;&gt;&gt; 豬肉<br />\n豬肉 + 牛肉精 &gt;&gt;&gt; 牛肉"},{"pid":"eaf8c313e39d4a43e972b939e34458f9be0d0e0e","tid":291444,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor